15
16#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_DNSKEY_48_C
17#define RDATA_GENERIC_DNSKEY_48_C
18
19#include <dst/dst.h>
20
21#define RRTYPE_DNSKEY_ATTRIBUTES (DNS_RDATATYPEATTR_DNSSEC)
22
23static inline isc_result_t
24fromtext_dnskey(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
25
26 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
27
28 return (generic_fromtext_key(rdclass, type, lexer, origin,
29 options, target, callbacks));
30}
31
32static inline isc_result_t
33totext_dnskey(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
34
35 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
36 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
37
38 return (generic_totext_key(rdata, tctx, target));
39}
40
41static inline isc_result_t
42fromwire_dnskey(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
43
44 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
45
46 return (generic_fromwire_key(rdclass, type, source, dctx,
47 options, target));
48}
49
50static inline isc_result_t
51towire_dnskey(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
52 isc_region_t sr;
53
54 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
55 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
56 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
57
58 UNUSED(cctx);
59
60 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
61 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
62}
63
64static inline int
65compare_dnskey(ARGS_COMPARE) {
66 isc_region_t r1;
67 isc_region_t r2;
68
69 REQUIRE(rdata1 != NULL);
70 REQUIRE(rdata2 != NULL);
71 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
72 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
73 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
74 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
75 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
76
77 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
78 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
79 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
80}
81
82static inline isc_result_t
83fromstruct_dnskey(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
84
85 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
86
87 return (generic_fromstruct_key(rdclass, type, source, target));
88}
89
90static inline isc_result_t
91tostruct_dnskey(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
92 dns_rdata_dnskey_t *dnskey = target;
93
94 REQUIRE(dnskey != NULL);
95 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
96 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
97
98 dnskey->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
99 dnskey->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
100 ISC_LINK_INIT(&dnskey->common, link);
101
102 return (generic_tostruct_key(rdata, target, mctx));
103}
104
105static inline void
106freestruct_dnskey(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
107 dns_rdata_dnskey_t *dnskey = (dns_rdata_dnskey_t *) source;
108
109 REQUIRE(dnskey != NULL);
110 REQUIRE(dnskey->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
111
112 generic_freestruct_key(source);
113}
114
115static inline isc_result_t
116additionaldata_dnskey(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
117
118 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
119
120 UNUSED(rdata);
121 UNUSED(add);
122 UNUSED(arg);
123
124 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
125}
126
127static inline isc_result_t
128digest_dnskey(ARGS_DIGEST) {
129 isc_region_t r;
130
131 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
132 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
133
134 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
135
136 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
137}
138
139static inline bool
140checkowner_dnskey(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
141
142 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
143
144 UNUSED(name);
145 UNUSED(type);
146 UNUSED(rdclass);
147 UNUSED(wildcard);
148
149 return (true);
150}
151
152static inline bool
153checknames_dnskey(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
154
155 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
156 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey);
157
158 UNUSED(rdata);
159 UNUSED(owner);
160 UNUSED(bad);
161
162 return (true);
163}
164
165static inline int
166casecompare_dnskey(ARGS_COMPARE) {
167
168 /*
169 * Treat ALG 253 (private DNS) subtype name case sensistively.
170 */
171 return (compare_dnskey(rdata1, rdata2));
172}

174#endif /* RDATA_GENERIC_DNSKEY_48_C */
